## Unified Messages API with SDK

**Covers Methods:**
- `fetchMessages()` - Query messages with type/token/user filters
- `createMessage()` - Create a CHAT or COMMENT message
- `updateMessage()` - Update message content (author only)
- `deleteMessage()` - Delete a message (author/owner/moderator)
- `getPinnedMessage()` - Get the pinned message for a token
- `pinMessage()` - Pin a message (owner/moderator)
- `unpinMessage()` - Unpin the current pinned message
- `getMessageStats()` - Get platform-wide message statistics

The unified messages API handles both `CHAT` (live stream chat) and `COMMENT` (token page comments) message types through a single /v1/messages endpoint.

### Fetch Messages

```typescript
import { createLaunchpadSDK } from '@gala-chain/launchpad-sdk';

const sdk = createLaunchpadSDK({ jwtToken: 'your-jwt-token' });

// Fetch chat messages for a token
const chatMessages = await sdk.fetchMessages({
  tokenName: 'anime',
  type: 'CHAT',
  limit: 50,
  page: 1,
});

// Fetch comment-type messages for a token
const comments = await sdk.fetchMessages({
  tokenName: 'anime',
  type: 'COMMENT',
  limit: 20,
});

// Fetch messages by a specific user
const userMessages = await sdk.fetchMessages({
  userAddress: 'eth|0x1234...',
  type: 'CHAT',
});
```

### Create Messages

```typescript
// Create a chat message (live stream chat)
const chatMsg = await sdk.createMessage({
  tokenName: 'anime',
  content: 'This token is amazing!',
  type: 'CHAT',
});
console.log('Created chat message:', chatMsg.id);

// Create a comment (token page)
const comment = await sdk.createMessage({
  tokenName: 'anime',
  content: 'Great project, bullish on this!',
  type: 'COMMENT',
});
console.log('Created comment:', comment.id);
```

### Update and Delete Messages

```typescript
// Update your own message
const updated = await sdk.updateMessage('message-uuid', {
  content: 'Updated message content',
});

// Delete a message (must be author, or have moderator/owner role)
await sdk.deleteMessage('message-uuid');
```

### Pin/Unpin Messages

```typescript
// Get the currently pinned message for a token
const pinned = await sdk.getPinnedMessage('anime');
if (pinned) {
  console.log('Pinned message:', pinned.content);
  console.log('Pinned by:', pinned.pinnedBy);
}

// Pin a message (requires owner or moderator role)
await sdk.pinMessage('message-uuid');

// Unpin the current pinned message
await sdk.unpinMessage('message-uuid');
```

### Get Message Statistics

```typescript
// Get platform-wide message statistics (admin/overseer only)
const stats = await sdk.getMessageStats();
console.log('Total CHAT messages:', stats.chatCount);
console.log('Total COMMENT messages:', stats.commentCount);
console.log('Messages today:', stats.todayCount);
```

